@* our cyberBot that appears at the home page *@
<h1 class="CyberBotHeading" style="font-size:250%">Ask CyberBoT</h1>

<div class="CyberBot">

	<p style="font-size:110%">
		Our user friendly Bot, if you have any querires regarding<br /> cyber threats or what are cyber threats, ask CyberBot.
		@* ask button *@
		<button onclick="toggleChat()" class="BotBtn">Ask CyberBot</button>


